Katie Holmes Instagram Photo of Suri Cruise March 2017 Suri Cruise Looks So Much Like Katie Holmes in This New Photo March 19, 2017 A post shared by Katie Holmes (@katieholmes212) on Mar 19, 2017 at 8:01am PDT 
Katie Holmes, is that you? On Sunday, the actress shared a photo of nearly 11-year-old daughter Suri Cruise hanging out with family on Instagram, and we immediately did a double take. Not only does she look all grown up, but she is the spitting image of Katie. "Love these sweethearts who inspire me with all of their accomplishments and beautiful hearts and for bringing so much light to all of our lives! ðŸ’•ðŸŽ€ðŸ’• #lalaland #losangeles #family #love #ontopoftheworld." #followyourdreams," Katie wrote. In addition to spending quality time with her daughter, Katie has also been hard at work promoting her new miniseries, The Kennedys: After Camelot .
